{"tid":1082761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個巴士傻人","createTime":"2019-03-29T07:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T05:11:01.000Z","uid":240771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e77293d773cd9443bca003f21333555b026735b","tid":1082761,"uid":240771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"拋個靚磚<br />\n平日每朝8點零鐘搭58M出葵芳，青松觀站都會有個傻佬上車，<br />\n一上到車就扮報站機，大大聲讀站名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有樣野更奇怪，就係報站機係（廣東話&gt;英文&gt;普通話），佢就（廣東話&gt;普通話&gt;英文）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有就係當個報站機報到屯門公路轉車站，佢就會加個「九龍方向」俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想講佢普通話可唔可以讀正D，「下一站是」讀撚到變咗「再見是」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「九龍方向」個英文報站機冇又唔自己查，求其𠼱過就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27eebf033e6e0940b7738d277649daf9f52514c2","tid":1082761,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"今日見到個叫「笑撚傻中右」"},{"pid":"fae3ab354b4846dd6aedb1603f474a5052dae202","tid":1082761,"uid":240771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27eebf033e6e0940b7738d277649daf9f52514c2","tid":1082761,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"今日見到個叫「笑撚傻中右」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"d4047d7dcdff9d9dd31e605614805d7b6d8db30d","tid":1082761,"uid":240771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7d78039f405efa3e3db58c903c5fc24573b849","tid":1082761,"uid":190739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"夜晚673往港島，偶然會見到有條友會由上層倒後行樓梯去下層落車，架車仲未埋站，真正極危險。"}]}